item.description: From the former director of "Shear Madness" comes Boston's funniest and most politically incorrect new stage comedy! FishNet-NetWorks.Net is a hilarious, 13 character parody of corporate meeting gone wrong! Think "Borat" meets "The Office!" This partially scripted and partially improvised show will truly have you in splits! Tickets and Info: See www.fishnet-networks.net Regular tickets are $40 pp but for this meetup, use PROMO CODE "MEETUP" online to get 50% off or just $20pp! Where: The Theater at Club Cafe, 209 Columbus Ave (Right near Back Bay Station) When: Friday, June 24, 7:30pm (but doors open at 7pm.)

group.name: New England Network for Women :: Cambridge
